quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  97,1,"Dájúdájú Àwa sọ al-Ƙur’ān kalẹ̀ nínú Òru Abiyì.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-’Isrọ̄’; 17:106."
  97,2,"Kí sì ni ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ Òru Abiyì?",""
  97,3,"Òru Abiyì lóore ju ẹgbẹ̀rún oṣù.",""
  97,4,"Àwọn mọlāika àti Jibrīl yó sì máa sọ̀kalẹ̀ nínú òru náà pẹ̀lú àṣẹ Olúwa wọn fún gbogbo ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀dá kọ̀ọ̀kan.",""
  97,5,"Àlàáfíà ni òru náà títí di àsìkò àfẹ̀mọ́júmọ́.",""
  98,1,"Àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú àwọn ahlul-kitāb àti àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ, wọn kò níí kúrò nínú àìgbàgbọ́ wọn títí di ìgbà tí ẹ̀rí tó yanjú yó fi máa dé ọ̀dọ̀ wọn.",""
  98,2,"Òjíṣẹ́ kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu yó (sì) máa ké àwọn tákàdá mímọ́.",""
  98,3,"Àwọn ìwé òfin tó fẹsẹ̀ rinlẹ̀ sì wà nínú rẹ̀.",""
  98,4,"Àwọn tí A fún ní tírà kò sì di ìjọ ọ̀tọ̀ọ̀tọ̀ àfi lẹ́yìn tí ẹ̀rí tó yanjú dé bá wọn.",""
  98,5,"Àwa kò sì pa wọ́n ní àṣẹ kan bí kò ṣe pé kí wọ́n jọ́sìn fún Allāhu lẹ́ni tí yóò máa ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ ẹ̀sìn fún Un,<sup>1</sup> lẹ́ni tí yóò dúró ṣinṣin nínú ẹ̀sìn. Kí wọ́n kírun, kí wọ́n sì yọ Zakāh. Ìyẹn sì ni ẹ̀sìn tó fẹsẹ̀ rinlẹ̀.","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Al-’a‘rọ̄f 7:29."
  98,6,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ (wọ̀nyí) nínú àwọn ahlul-kitāb àti àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ, wọn yóò wà nínú Iná. Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn, àwọn ni ẹ̀dá tó burú jùlọ.",""
  98,7,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo (ìyẹn, àwọn mùsùlùmí), tí wọ́n sì ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ rere, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn, àwọn ni ẹ̀dá tó dára jùlọ.",""
